&lt;p id="uVIljm"&gt;The app also automatically archives old tabs, blocks ads by default, and gets rid of data-tracking popups, which has me tempted to switch away from Edge. While Arc initially launched as a Mac-only desktop browser, the &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/28/24053882/arc-search-browser-web-app-ios"&gt;Arc Search app&lt;/a&gt; launched widely...&lt;/p&gt;
